{"tid":329551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"登月48周年 SpaceX提倡建月球基地","createTime":"2017-07-20T12:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T14:06:53.000Z","uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c87991b08124a082b83ce223d36f619253d5f53","tid":329551,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc&d=uR%2FFaE%2BzS7%2FmBatKk%2BlWOf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0157eda6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc</a><br />\n人類登月48周年　SpaceX提倡建月球基地｜即時新聞｜國際｜<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=uR%2FFaE%2BzS7%2FmBatKk%2BlWOf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=55f31728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網<br />\n周四（20日）為人類登月48周年，一袋由首位登陸月球的太空人所收集的月球麈埃，將於美國東岸時間周四早上11時進行拍賣。而美國太空探索科技公司（SpaceX）行政總裁兼始創人馬斯克周三（19日）在一個研討會上表示，若果要令公眾對太空旅遊更感興趣，就有必要建立一個月球基地，更稱對很多人不知道或不理解國際太空站的有趣之處感到遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克期望有一日通過新型火箭，能把普通市民送上太空，又稱第一批的乘客將要非常勇敢。針對月球基地的構想，馬斯克說：「這將會是阿波羅計劃夢想的延續，我想人們亦會非常期待。」<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克早前曾透露，最初創立SpaceX的目標為讓人類成為多星球的物種，更打算在不久之後將人類送上火星，並計劃在洛杉磯挖地下隧道，然後將有關科技應用在設計能在火星挖掘的設備上。<br />\n<br />\n| <a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=uR%2FFaE%2BzS7%2FmBatKk%2BlWOf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=55f31728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網<br />\n切換到豐富的查看<br />\n人類月球日| 今天，你也可以在月球踏上自己的「一小步」 &mdash; 中國新聞網 (新聞發布) (註冊)<br />\n馬斯克：人類需要在月球建立基地 &mdash; 香港新浪財經<br />\n今天是人類月球日，還記得48年前的今天人類第一次登月成功嗎？ &mdash; Knowing (新聞發布)"},{"pid":"9a90852a913f8c9b242f37c59bfb9daabd5d0c93","tid":329551,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"月球有外星人想搶人地盤呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056ffe4ae40b76064f50f6346ae0455f144c9f98","tid":329551,"uid":60648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"月面基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e57c92e0061bab48f79f9209944f60da054fd46","tid":329551,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:48:14.000Z","msg":"我想"},{"pid":"d768669c60ac6d6c2b8b4e7e90f3683aa350af9e","tid":329551,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}